In this case what is recommended to have the template as a string in python, so:
```python
template_body = {
  "template": '''{
    "query": {
      "terms": {
        "test": {{#toJson}}anArray{{/toJson}}
      }
    }
  }'''
}
```

Then it will get properly serialized as:
```json
{"template": "{\n    \"query\": {\n      \"terms\": {\n        \"test\": {{#toJson}}anArray{{/toJson}}\n      }\n    }\n  }"}
```

Which is what the API will accept.

Hope this helps!

